title: Fried green tomatoes
description: Evelyn Couch is having trouble in her marriage, and no one seems to take her seriously. While in a nursing home visiting relatives, she meets Ninny Threadgoode, an outgoing old woman, who tells her the story of Idgie Threadgoode, a young woman in 1920&#039;s Alabama. Through Idgie&#039;s inspiring life, Evelyn learns to be more assertive and builds a lasting friendship of her own with Ninny
